; Coverage for report.cc limit combining with & in commodities_report
; When commodities_report strips state predicates from a compound limit,
; remaining non-state terms are re-joined with &
; Three limit terms: "cleared" (state pred, stripped) + "total>0" + "commodity=~/AAPL/"
; After stripping, the two non-state terms are joined: (total>0)&(commodity=~/AAPL/)

P 2024/01/01 AAPL $150.00
P 2024/01/01 GOOG $100.00

2024/01/01 * Buy
    Assets:Stocks    10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Stocks    5 GOOG @ $100.00
    Assets:Cash

test commodities --cleared --limit 'total>0' --limit 'commodity=~/AAPL/'
$
AAPL
end test
